text: It seems as if the module `nilearn.decomposition` has remained undocumented, both in the _reference guide_ http://nilearn.github.io/modules/reference.html as in the _user guide_ http://nilearn.github.io/user_guide.html (referencing the `FastICA` function from the `scikit-learn.decomposition` module here but not `CanICA`)
title: [documentation] module `̀nilearn.decomposition`
